# ===========================================
# Project: Amara Home Management System (AHMS)
# ===========================================

## Project Overview

Amara Home Management System (AHMS) is a modern web application designed to manage and maintain a single luxury home or villa.

The purpose of this system is to help homeowners keep track of everything related to their house, including maintenance schedules, service contracts, warranties, repair history, service companies, expenses, documents, inspections, and reminders.

Instead of manually remembering maintenance dates or searching for contractor details, the system provides a centralized dashboard with automated reminders, notifications, and complete maintenance history.

The goal is to digitize home management and make maintaining a luxury property simple, organized, and efficient.

This is NOT a property management system for multiple properties.

This system is designed for ONE home or villa.

