---

# Project Goals

The application should help the homeowner:

• Keep track of every maintenance contract.

• Know when maintenance is due.

• Know when warranties expire.

• Store all company information.

• Store all invoices and documents.

• Receive notifications before maintenance dates.

• Track repair history.

• Track maintenance expenses.

• Keep the house in excellent condition.

---

# Frontend Development (Phase 1)

Only frontend should be developed initially.

DO NOT implement backend functionality.

Use mock JSON data where required.

Focus on:

• Professional UI
• Responsive Design
• Reusable Components
• Clean Folder Structure
• Proper State Management
• Beautiful UX
• Dark/Light Theme Ready

